Package server

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Holds data sent from MOPED to be used in calculations for ACC and platooning.
    DataGrabber  
    FixedDataQueue  
    InputInterpreter
    This class interprets the JSON object sent from the app that contains steering signal and whether ACC and platooning are active or not.
    ProgramManager
    Handles threads for ACC and platooning.
    Start
    Main class of the server.
    ThreadManager
    Manages all threads that are needed for connecting to the MOPED and the app.
